{"tid":1785696,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連now記者都被拒入境澳門","createTime":"2019-12-16T14:49:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-16T14:51:07.000Z","uid":125168,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c6627164aa1297409ae804c6cb38e460af3c2c73","tid":1785696,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T14:49:16.000Z","msg":"now記者在港珠澳人工島公安檢查站被拒入境澳門<br />\n<br />\nnow新聞台報道，採訪隊經港珠澳大橋打算入境澳門，準備採訪澳門回歸工作，其中記者在東人工島內地公安的檢查站，被內地邊防人員拒絕入境澳門，攝影師則順利過關。邊防人員未有向被拒入境記者解釋原因，只是說情況會維持幾天。 now新聞台說，該名記者早前已向澳門當局報名，參與澳門回歸採訪活動。他與攝影師乘坐金巴，下午抵達東人工島內地公安檢查站，記者在櫃位向邊防人員出示回鄉證及身分證，之後就被帶到臨時等候區，個多小時後邊防人員拒絕他入境，並搜查他的隨身物品及查詢到訪澳門的目的。邊防人員詢問記者背景並作筆錄，全程以攝影機錄影，之後安排金巴將記者送返香港。<br />\n<br />\n2019-12-16 22:41:06 RTHK"},{"pid":"c880745d7dcfa257d05b20783d30d13df0ae8230","tid":1785696,"uid":202524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T14:50:17.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 借個位黎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">德國戰線要人</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">目標：5萬人聯署</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">依家差2萬人咋！！！</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇時間啦25號截止，極度要人幫手!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1782422\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1782422</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"935218c26f1e7a68fe50466